sequenceDiagram
    participant UserA as User A
    participant UserB as User B
    participant Group as Group Call
    participant Server as Server
    participant QualityControl as Quality Control

    UserA->>Server: Initiate call (User B)
    Server-->>UserB: Notify call (User A)
    UserB->>Server: Accept call
    Server-->>UserA: Connect call (User B)
    
    UserA->>QualityControl: Monitor call quality
    UserB->>QualityControl: Monitor call quality
    QualityControl-->>UserA: Adjust quality settings
    QualityControl-->>UserB: Adjust quality settings

    UserA->>Server: Add User C to call
    Server-->>Group: Notify User C to join
    UserC->>Server: Join call
    Server-->>Group: Connect User C

    UserA->>Group: Mute microphone
    UserB->>Group: Turn off video
    UserC->>Group: Share screen

    UserA->>Server: End call
    Server-->>Group: Disconnect all participants